content.raw:
I tried compiling it and got a bunch of warnings. I've written a patch to eliminate most of them, but I don't have access to this fork. So I've [uploaded the patch here](http://dl.dropbox.com/u/96660379/gazebo_jlee02_compile_warnings.patch).

I also had trouble linking with RTQL8, since it didn't appear to build shared libraries. What are the cmake variables we're supposed to use when building RTQL8?
